title: Daily Review With Clay and Buck - Jul 28 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review With Clay and Buck - Jul 28 2022
description:
The economy has contracted for the second straight quarter in Q2 - but we're not in a recession! The Chinese are unhappy that Speaker Pelosi may be going to Taiwan. Why is she going there now? Clay calls in from the Bedminster golf course to update us on the LIV Pro-Am. AZ Gubernatorial Candidate Kari Lake updates us on the state of the race.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
